title: Cylichna gouldii
content:
Cylichna gouldii is a species of very small sea snail, a small bubble snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Cylichnidae.

This bubble snail lives in the Western Atlantic Ocean and has been found in Nova Scotia, Maine and Massachusetts. [1]
